Title: $U_q(sl(n))$ Difference Operator Realization
Author: Azizollah Shafiekhani (ISTPM, Tehran, Iran)
Comments: 12 pages
Report-no: IPM-94-052, SUTP/2/73
Subj-class: High Energy Physics - Theory; Quantum Algebra
Journal-ref: Mod.Phys.Lett. A9 (1994) 3273-3284
\\
  A unified and systematic scheme for constraction of differential opreator
realization of any irreducible representation of $sl(n)$ is developed. The
$q$-analogue of this unified scheme is used to constract $q$-difference
operator realization of any irreducible representation of $U_q(sl(n))$.
Explicit results for $U_q(sl(2))$, $U_q(sl(3))$ and $U_q(sl(n))$ are given.
